# FUTURE_DS_03
Marketing funnel and conversion analysis using R and Power BI

 📊 Marketing Funnel & Conversion Analysis

🔍 Project Overview

This project analyzes a marketing funnel to understand how customers move from leads to conversions using real-world campaign data.

🎯 Objectives

* Identify drop-off points in the funnel
* Analyze conversion rates
* Compare marketing channel performance
* Provide data-driven recommendations

🛠 Tools Used

* R (data cleaning & analysis)
* Power BI (dashboard & visualization)

📊 Key Insights

* Overall conversion rate is low (~12%)
* Direct contact channels perform better
* Excessive campaign contact reduces conversion
* Certain customer segments have higher conversion rates

📁 Files Included

* Dataset (cleaned)
* R analysis script
* Power BI dashboard

🚀 Outcome

This project demonstrates practical skills in marketing analytics, data visualization, and business insight generation.
